{"tid":790924,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"全盛時期嘅復仇者聯盟聯手可唔可以打敗家燕媽媽","createTime":"2018-08-23T11:25:35.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-23T17:02:42.000Z","uid":31219,"like":21,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"d6a5f132392732b8627f17c4c3a8f10e2cee030d","tid":790924,"uid":31219,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T11:25:35.000Z","msg":"復仇者聯盟嘅強處相信大家都知所以唔講<br />\n<br />\n以下講下家燕媽媽嘅能力<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/23/192301_549fd3eb394fa2cec3c61921caaa7493.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F23%2F192301_549fd3eb394fa2cec3c61921caaa7493.png&h=a25221ee&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n飛行：好基本嘅超級英雄能力，唔多講<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/23/192306_8b6f8d98ca647cc6e0f1776dac5bc748.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F23%2F192306_8b6f8d98ca647cc6e0f1776dac5bc748.png&h=7a428f80&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n激光：可以爆鐵閘，強度估計同Vision差唔多<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/23/192312_ef79fbcc7492a4f604ffc69014a9b9d4.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F23%2F192312_ef79fbcc7492a4f604ffc69014a9b9d4.png&h=d7be863e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n肉體控制：可以控制人跳舞，相信控制復仇者聯盟內鬥唔係問題<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/23/192327_af5d494436b8face3aa64726d325223c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F23%2F192327_af5d494436b8face3aa64726d325223c.png&h=744339b1&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n照明：其實即係激光。但代表家燕媽媽可以自由控制自己超能力嘅強度，好多超級英雄都做唔到<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/23/192334_c21214063323fe4fe2b78ba303faee54.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F23%2F192334_c21214063323fe4fe2b78ba303faee54.png&h=81ba92c3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n震裂塊地：一腳可以踩爛塊地，相信只有Hulk可以一戰<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/23/192339_0aafaa931422a9b1f85b0270dd136716.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F23%2F192339_0aafaa931422a9b1f85b0270dd136716.png&h=2bcad9e7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n刀槍不入：可以彈開子彈<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/23/192345_02f566629baf66c2c67b9f9a255a0b5b.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F23%2F192345_02f566629baf66c2c67b9f9a255a0b5b.png&h=fbaae375&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n思想控制：令壞人變成好人，善用嘅話可以好似Loki令Hawkeye倒戈、Scarlet Witch令Hulk發癲<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/08/23/192446_18d0d83273f92d1e77f45446d3fa4788.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F08%2F23%2F192446_18d0d83273f92d1e77f45446d3fa4788.png&h=f9949509&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n遠距離操控物件：劇中用嚟解繩，實戰中可以令Ironman嘅裝甲、武器短路<br />\n<br />\n總括以上能力，面對家傳戶曉嘅家燕媽媽，復仇者聯盟聯手有冇一分嘅勝算？<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/NyfS9-wlMjM\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FNyfS9-wlMjM&d=9KtZC7Xczbv2fjYgGjHB7ZZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=bfd98bd0\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/NyfS9-wlMjM</a><br />\n利申：非打手"},{"pid":"ed4a589660466fc869556fafed13e9e18a8bb2c5","tid":790924,"uid":44031,"like":3,"dislike":18,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T11:34:35.000Z","msg":"雖然你好用心 但係真係有幾分老尷<br />\n繼續努力"},{"pid":"bb1d08b84243a61ee602afbe908e94a0918d5e26","tid":790924,"uid":15494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T16:53:23.000Z","msg":"唔講咁多"},{"pid":"b5a15b2a35b7880255506fe6772b4364393a2909","tid":790924,"uid":20914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-23T17:02:42.000Z","msg":"難啲<br />\nCaptain Nancy勁太多"}]}